Gotta keep driving

Wanna stay focused

Can’t think about
What I left —
Behind

Wanna keep moving

Can’t stop saying

Something good
Has
— gotta come

They found each other’s
Arms:
Just to hold onto
Just to hold on to

So they know:
They’re not alone

I’m not alone


